        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Dear Deal Team,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A Non Deal Approval record has been granted approval.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description: &lt;/strong&gt;{!varTriggeringDeal.leaseworks__Description__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary Of Approval Request: &lt;/strong&gt;{!varTriggeringDeal.pro_Summary_Of_Approval_Request__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Comments: &lt;/strong&gt;{!varTriggeringDeal.pro_Financial_Comments__c}&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can view the full details and take action by clicking the link: &lt;a href=&quot;https://leaseworks-carlyle.lightning.force.com/{!varTriggeringDeal.Id}&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;View Non Deal Approval in Salesforce&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kind regards,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Salesforce System Notification&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This message was generated automatically. For assistance, please contact your Salesforce administrator.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
